Items.mt: We are always laughed at by the Jianfeng Sect for having a false appearance, not as strong as their sword. We are shamed by Fei Bai for being clumsy, unlike them who can always win by surprise.

Items.r: 我们总被剑锋派耻笑虚有其表，不若他们的剑一样有力度。被飞白耻笑身法笨拙，不似他们总能以奇致胜。
